      <section class="field field-name-field-rating field-type-fivestar field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-_custom_display"><h2 class="field-label">Rate this Article:&nbsp;</h2><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="schema:aggregateRating" typeof="schema:AggregateRating"><form class="fivestar-widget" action="/content/privacy-policy" method="post" id="fivestar-custom-widget" accept-charset="UTF-8"><div><div  class="clearfix fivestar-average-text fivestar-average-stars fivestar-form-item fivestar-sun"><div class="form-item form-type-fivestar form-item-vote">
